    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! If you've been searching for your dream ride, you've finally found it! This car is an absolute beauty and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've taken such good care of it\u2014it\u2019s been totally babied and is in pristine shape inside and out. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. You won't find another one this clean! Come take a look and see for yourself!",
